msgid "# Batch Invariance"
msgstr "# 批次不变性"

msgid ""
"Batch invariance is currently in beta. Some features are still under active development.\n"
"    Track progress and planned improvements at <https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/issues/5487>"
msgstr ""
"批次不变性目前处于测试阶段。部分功能仍在积极开发中。\n"
"    请访问 <https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/issues/5487> 跟踪进展和计划改进"

msgid ""
"To install the batch invariance custom operator library, set `VLLM_BATCH_INVARIANT=1` before building vllm-ascend.\n"
"    For installation instructions, see <https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/docs/source/installation.md#set-up-using-python>"
msgstr ""
"要安装批次不变性自定义算子库，请在构建 vllm-ascend 之前设置 `VLLM_BATCH_INVARIANT=1`。\n"
"    安装说明请参见 <https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/docs/source/installation.md#set-up-using-python>"

msgid ""
"This document shows how to enable batch invariance in vLLM-Ascend. Batch "
"invariance ensures that the output of a model is deterministic and "
"independent of the batch size or the order of requests in a batch."
msgstr "本文档介绍如何在 vLLM-Ascend 中启用批次不变性。批次不变性确保模型的输出是确定性的，并且与批次大小或批次中请求的顺序无关。"

msgid "## Motivation"
msgstr "## 动机"

msgid "Batch invariance is crucial for several use cases:"
msgstr "批次不变性在以下几种使用场景中至关重要："

msgid ""
"- **Framework debugging**: Deterministic outputs make it easier to debug issues in the inference framework, as the same input will always produce the same output regardless of batching.\n"
"- **Model debugging**: Helps identify issues in model implementations by ensuring consistent behavior across different batch configurations.\n"
"- **Reinforcement Learning (RL)**: RL training often requires deterministic rollouts for reproducibility and stable training.\n"
"- **Large-scale inference systems**: Systems that use vLLM as a component benefit from deterministic behavior for testing, validation, and consistency guarantees."
msgstr ""
"- **框架调试**：确定性输出使得推理框架中的问题调试更加容易，因为无论批处理如何，相同的输入总是产生相同的输出。\n"
"- **模型调试**：通过确保不同批次配置下行为一致，帮助识别模型实现中的问题。\n"
"- **强化学习 (RL)**：RL 训练通常需要确定性的推演以实现可复现性和稳定训练。\n"
"- **大规模推理系统**：将 vLLM 作为组件的系统受益于确定性行为，用于测试、验证和一致性保证。"

msgid "## Hardware Requirements"
msgstr "## 硬件要求"

msgid ""
"Batch invariance currently requires Ascend Atlas A2 and A3 inference products NPUs.\n"
"We will support Ascend 950 Products and other NPUs in the future."
msgstr ""
"批次不变性目前需要 Ascend Atlas A2 和 A3 推理产品的 NPU。\n"
"我们将在未来支持 Ascend 950 产品及其他 NPU。"

msgid "## Software Requirements"
msgstr "## 软件要求"

msgid ""
"Batch invariance requires a custom operator library for Atlas A2 and A3 "
"inference products, and users need to set `VLLM_BATCH_INVARIANT=1` before "
"building vllm-ascend to install the batch invariance custom operator library"
" during the installation process."
msgstr ""
"批次不变性需要 Atlas A2 和 A3 推理产品的自定义算子库，用户需要在构建 vllm-ascend 之前设置 "
"`VLLM_BATCH_INVARIANT=1`，以便在安装过程中安装批次不变性自定义算子库。"

msgid "## Enabling Batch Invariance"
msgstr "## 启用批次不变性"

msgid ""
"Batch invariance can be enabled by setting the `VLLM_BATCH_INVARIANT` "
"environment variable to `1`:"
msgstr "可以通过将 `VLLM_BATCH_INVARIANT` 环境变量设置为 `1` 来启用批次不变性："

msgid "### Online Inference (Server Mode)"
msgstr "### 在线推理（服务器模式）"

msgid "To start a vLLM server with batch invariance enabled:"
msgstr "启动启用了批次不变性的 vLLM 服务器："

msgid "Then use the OpenAI-compatible client:"
msgstr "然后使用 OpenAI 兼容的客户端："

msgid "### Offline Inference"
msgstr "### 离线推理"

msgid "For offline batch inference with batch invariance:"
msgstr "对于具有批次不变性的离线批次推理："

msgid "## Tested Models"
msgstr "## 已测试模型"

msgid "Batch invariance has been tested and verified on the following models:"
msgstr "批次不变性已在以下模型上进行了测试和验证："

msgid ""
"- **Qwen3 (Dense)**: `Qwen/Qwen3-1.7B`, `Qwen/Qwen3-8B`\n"
"- **Qwen3 (MoE)**: `Qwen/Qwen3-30B-A3B`, `Qwen/Qwen3-235B-A22B`"
msgstr ""
"- **Qwen3 (密集模型)**：`Qwen/Qwen3-1.7B`、`Qwen/Qwen3-8B`\n"
"- **Qwen3 (MoE)**：`Qwen/Qwen3-30B-A3B`、`Qwen/Qwen3-235B-A22B`"

msgid ""
"Other models may also work, but these have been explicitly validated. If you"
" encounter issues with a specific model, please report them on the [GitHub "
"issue tracker](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/issues/new/choose)."
msgstr ""
"其他模型也可能适用，但这些模型已明确验证。如果您在特定模型上遇到问题，请在 [GitHub "
"问题跟踪器](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/issues/new/choose) 上报告。"

msgid "## Implementation Details"
msgstr "## 实现细节"

msgid "When batch invariance is enabled, vLLM:"
msgstr "当启用批次不变性时，vLLM："

msgid ""
"1. Uses deterministic kernel implementations for attention and other operations\n"
"2. Ensures consistent numerical behavior across different batch sizes\n"
"3. Disables certain optimizations that may introduce non-determinism"
msgstr ""
"1. 对注意力和其他操作使用确定性内核实现\n"
"2. 确保不同批次大小下数值行为一致\n"
"3. 禁用可能引入非确定性的某些优化"

msgid ""
"The batch invariance attention operators currently do not support\n"
"    `FULL'、'FULL_DECODE_ONLY` cudagraph mode."
msgstr ""
"批次不变性注意力算子目前不支持\n"
"    `FULL'、'FULL_DECODE_ONLY` cudagraph 模式。"

msgid ""
"Enabling batch invariance may impact performance compared to the default "
"non-deterministic mode. This trade-off is intentional to guarantee "
"reproducibility."
msgstr "与默认的非确定性模式相比，启用批次不变性可能会影响性能。这种权衡是故意的，以保证可复现性。"

msgid "## Future Improvements"
msgstr "## 未来改进"

msgid ""
"The batch invariance feature is under active development. Planned "
"improvements include:"
msgstr "批次不变性功能正在积极开发中。计划中的改进包括："

msgid ""
"- Support for additional NPUs series\n"
"- Support `FULL'、'FULL_DECODE_ONLY` cudagraph mode with batch invariance attention operators\n"
"- Expanded model coverage\n"
"- Performance optimizations\n"
"- Additional testing and validation"
msgstr ""
"- 支持更多 NPU 系列\n"
"- 支持带有批次不变性注意力算子的 `FULL'、'FULL_DECODE_ONLY` cudagraph 模式\n"
"- 扩展模型覆盖范围\n"
"- 性能优化\n"
"- 更多测试和验证"

msgid ""
"For the latest status and to contribute ideas, see the [tracking "
"issue](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/issues/5487)."
msgstr ""
"有关最新状态和贡献想法，请参见 [跟踪问题](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/issues/5487)。"
